premise_source_doc_sentence: The film 's storyline is based in part upon the Hellboy : Wake the Devil storyline from the original comics .
Also included on the DVD is the short film Iron Shoes , which is based on the Hellboy story of the same name .

Hellboy : The Crooked Man and Others is the tenth collected edition of Mike Mignola 's comic book series Hellboy , collecting Hellboy : The Crooked Man # 1-3 , Hellboy : In the Chapel of Moloch , Hellboy : They That Go Down to the Sea in Ships and the story `` The Mole '' from `` Free Comic Book Day 2008 : Hellboy . ''

Hellboy : The Storm and the Fury is the twelfth collected edition of Mike Mignola 's comic book series Hellboy , collecting `` Hellboy : The Storm # 1-3 '' and `` Hellboy : The Fury # 1-3 '' , with the partition into two limited series  (  series whose actions are set minutes apart from each other  )  intended to accommodate an anticipated production gap of several months that eventually saw the story 's first three issues published from July -- September 2010 and its last three , following the publication of several other Hellboy projects , from May -- August 2011 .
Hellboy : Blood and Iron is the second in the Hellboy Animated series  (  the first being Hellboy : Sword of Storms  )  , written by Tad Stones and Mike Mignola .
